      }
    },
    "content": [
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "*Disclosure: This post contains affiliate links. If you purchase through them, I may earn a commission at no extra cost to you.*",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I've tested dozens of CRMs over the years. Most of them promise simplicity and deliver complexity. They want you to abandon your inbox, learn a new interface, and copy-paste contact info between tabs like it's 2009.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://get.streak.com/mpug8tw2pl8n"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Then I found ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Streak",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ". And everything changed.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Streak isn't a CRM that *integrates* with Gmail. It *is* a CRM inside Gmail. Your pipelines, your email tracking, your follow-up automations—they all live where you already spend your day. No tab-switching. No context loss. No friction.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Over 750,000 professionals and 4,000+ companies (including Spotify, Uber, Harvard, and Y Combinator) trust Streak to manage their sales, hiring, partnerships, and support workflows. That's not hype—it's proof.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Let me walk you through exactly why Streak deserves a spot in your browser.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The Core Idea: Your Inbox Is Your CRM",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Here's what most CRM tools get wrong: they assume your workflow starts in *their* app. But for millions of professionals, the real workflow starts in email. You send a pitch, wait for a reply, schedule a call, send a follow-up—all from your inbox.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Streak recognized this years ago. Instead of dragging you out of Gmail, they built a full CRM layer on top of it.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What does that look like in practice?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Pipelines",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " appear as a sidebar or a dedicated view right inside Gmail.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Contact records",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " auto-populate from email threads—no manual data entry.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Email tracking",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " shows you when someone opens your message, what device they used, and how many times.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Mail merge",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " lets you send personalized bulk emails without leaving your compose window.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Task reminders and follow-ups",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " trigger based on pipeline stage changes or time delays.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The result is a CRM that feels like a natural extension of something you already use every single day. There's no learning curve worth mentioning. If you can use Gmail, you can use Streak. That's a bold claim, but it holds up.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/how-to-use-streak"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you want a detailed walkthrough, check our ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "step-by-step Streak tutorial",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Features That Make Teams Switch",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Streak packs serious functionality into a deceptively simple interface. Here are the features I see teams actually using—and loving.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Shared Pipelines",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This is where Streak shines for teams. You can create pipelines for sales, hiring, fundraising, real estate, event planning—whatever your workflow looks like—and share them with specific teammates. Everyone sees the same data. Everyone knows the status of every deal.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Each pipeline is fully customizable: rename stages, add fields, set probabilities, color-code by priority. I've seen agencies build client onboarding pipelines, HR teams build candidate tracking pipelines, and solo founders build investor outreach pipelines—all in Streak, all in Gmail.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Mail Merge",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Streak's mail merge is one of the best I've used. You can pull contacts directly from a pipeline, personalize each email with merge fields (name, company, last interaction date), and schedule sends. The merge runs from your actual Gmail account—not a third-party server—so deliverability stays high.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Open tracking, link tracking, and reply detection all come built in. You'll know exactly who engaged and who needs a nudge.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l2",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/streak-tips"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Want to master this feature? Our ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Streak tips and best practices",
            "marks": [
              "l2"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " guide covers advanced mail merge workflows.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Email Tracking & Snippets",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Real-time notifications tell you the moment a recipient opens your email or clicks a link. That kind of signal is gold for sales reps and founders doing outreach.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Snippets (Streak's version of templates) let you save your best-performing emails and insert them with a keyboard shortcut. Combine snippets with mail merge, and you've got a lightweight but powerful outreach engine.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Automations",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Streak's automation engine lets you trigger actions based on pipeline events. When a deal moves to \"Proposal Sent,\" automatically schedule a follow-up task for three days later. When someone replies to a mail merge, move them to the \"Engaged\" stage. These little automations save hours every week.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The Pro+ plan unlocks advanced automations and integrations with tools like Slack, Zapier, and Google Sheets. If you're running a serious pipeline, that tier is worth it.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "AI Features",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Streak has rolled out AI credits across all plans. These help you draft emails, summarize thread histories, and generate follow-up suggestions based on conversation context. It's a smart use of AI—not gimmicky, genuinely useful. The Pro plan includes 20 credits per user per month, while Enterprise bumps that to 500.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Reports & Dashboards",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "On Pro+ and Enterprise plans, you get advanced reporting: pipeline velocity, conversion rates by stage, team performance breakdowns, and forecast data. The reports update in real time as your pipeline changes. No spreadsheets required.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l3",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/streak-use-cases"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Curious about how these compare in different workflows? Our ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Streak use cases article",
            "marks": [
              "l3"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " breaks down real-world scenarios.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "New & Highlighted Features",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Streak keeps shipping updates that make the tool more powerful without bloating it. Here's what's recent and worth your attention.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "AI-Powered Email Drafting",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": The AI assistant can now compose first drafts of outreach emails, follow-ups, and meeting requests based on the context of your existing thread. It learns your tone over time. Twenty credits per month on Pro feels generous for light use; heavy users will want Pro+.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Enhanced Mail Merge with A/B Testing",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": You can now test subject lines and body copy across segments of your mail merge list. Streak tracks which variant performs better on open and reply rates. For outreach-heavy teams, this is a game-changer.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Improved Mobile Experience",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": The mobile app now supports full pipeline editing, not just viewing. Stage changes, notes, and task completions work smoothly on iOS and Android. If you close deals on the go, this matters.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Deeper Google Workspace Integration",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": Streak now syncs with Google Calendar for meeting scheduling, Google Sheets for data export, and Google Drive for attaching files directly to pipeline boxes. The ecosystem feels tighter than ever.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Custom Roles & Permissions (Enterprise)",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": Large teams can now define granular access controls—view-only for interns, full edit for managers, admin-only for sensitive pipelines. This was a top-requested feature, and Streak delivered.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l4",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/streak-new-features"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "For the latest feature drops, keep an eye on our ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Streak new features page",
            "marks": [
              "l4"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
            "marks": []
