            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Who Is Streak Ideal For?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Streak isn't trying to be everything to everyone. That's a strength, not a limitation. Here's who gets the most value from it.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Solo Founders & Freelancers",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": If you're managing client relationships, investor outreach, or freelance gigs from Gmail, Streak replaces a standalone CRM without adding complexity. The free tier is genuinely usable for light pipelines.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Small Sales Teams (2–20 people)",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": Shared pipelines, mail merge, and email tracking make Streak a lean sales CRM that doesn't require a dedicated admin. Setup takes minutes, not days. No need for a Salesforce consultant.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Agencies & Consultants",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": Client onboarding, project tracking, and lead management all fit neatly into Streak's pipeline model. Multiple pipelines per account means you can run different workflows side by side.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Recruiters & HR Teams",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": Candidate tracking through hiring stages is a natural fit. Pair it with mail merge for bulk candidate outreach and email tracking to know who's engaged.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Real Estate Professionals",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": Property pipelines, buyer/seller tracking, and follow-up automations map perfectly to Streak's architecture. Several top-producing agents I know use it daily.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Nonprofits & Fundraisers",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": Donor pipelines, grant application tracking, and volunteer coordination—Streak handles these workflows without the overhead of enterprise CRMs.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If your work lives in email, Streak fits. It's that simple.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
