      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I've recommended Streak to founders, sales reps, agency owners, and recruiters. Every single one had the same reaction: *\"Why didn't I find this sooner?\"*",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The reason is simple. Streak removes the biggest friction point in CRM adoption—actually using it. When your CRM lives inside the tool you already open 50 times a day, adoption isn't a problem. Your team doesn't need training. Your data doesn't get stale. Your follow-ups don't fall through the cracks.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Streak is proof that the best software doesn't ask you to change your habits. It meets you where you are.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l9",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://get.streak.com/mpug8tw2pl8n"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you're tired of juggling a separate CRM tab, tired of copy-pasting email addresses into contact records, tired of missing follow-ups because your to-do list lives in a different app—",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "give Streak a try",
            "marks": [
              "l9"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ". The free tier costs nothing. The paid plans pay for themselves in recovered deals and saved hours.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
