    "image_prompt": "Editorial tech thumbnail, 16:9. Incorporate the brand logo fetched from https://logo.clearbit.com/streak.com as the clean focal element over a soft amber-to-cream gradient (Notion + Apple aesthetic). A person working at a laptop with Gmail open, colorful CRM pipeline stages visible in the sidebar, modern home office with warm lighting. Glassmorphism cards, soft volumetric light, generous negative space for a title, no embedded text, no watermark. --ar 16:9 --style raw",
    "faq_items": [
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Is Streak really free to use?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes. Streak offers a free tier with basic CRM features, email tracking, and limited pipeline boxes. It's great for solo users who want lightweight contact and deal management inside Gmail without paying anything. Paid plans unlock shared pipelines, mail merge, automations, and AI features.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How is Streak different from Salesforce or HubSpot?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Streak lives entirely inside Gmail—there's no separate app to learn or switch to. While Salesforce and HubSpot are powerful standalone CRMs, Streak eliminates the friction of context-switching. For teams that run their business from email, Streak's native Gmail integration means faster adoption, less training, and more consistent data entry.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Can I use Streak with Google Workspace (business Gmail)?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Absolutely. Streak is built specifically for Google Workspace. It integrates with Gmail, Google Calendar, Google Sheets, and Google Drive. Shared pipelines and team features work seamlessly across Workspace accounts, making it ideal for business teams of any size.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Does Streak work on mobile?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes. Streak has mobile apps for both iOS and Android. Recent updates have added full pipeline editing on mobile, so you can update deal stages, add notes, and complete tasks from your phone. Email tracking and notifications also work on mobile.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
